Class PatternMatcherRootContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.query.tooling.ui.queryexplorer.content.matcher.BaseContent<ParentType>

        • org.eclipse.viatra.query.tooling.ui.queryexplorer.content.matcher.PatternMatcherRootContent

  • public class PatternMatcherRootContent
extends CompositeContent<RootContent,PatternMatcherContent>
    A top level element in the QueryExplorer's tree viewer, which is actually displayed. Instances of this class are always associated with an instance of PatternMatcherRootContentKey. The child elements of this CompositeContent will consist of PatternMatcherContent instances.

      • dispose

        public void dispose()
        Description copied from class: BaseContent
        Disposes of this content. It is the method's responsibility to call dispose on all child elements. Important: do NOT call dispose on the children observable collection as it will be invoked when the observable tree viewer processes the list diffs. This implementation should only release those resources (matchers / engines / etc) which are directly bound to this content.
        Overrides:
